    <title>elasticsearch 根据条件对数组字段进行删除</title>
    <link href="http://skymilong.cn/2019/08/28/elasticsearch%20%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%AD%97%E6%AE%B5%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4/"/>
    <id>http://skymilong.cn/2019/08/28/elasticsearch 根据条件对数组字段进行删除/</id>
    <published>2019-08-28T05:45:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-08-28T05:59:19.468Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>因为需求改动，必须要去删除一个数组的其中一个对象.<br>如下例子，要根据 ID 去删除。一般的修改可以直接 update，但是 cars 里面是数组，不好更新。</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cars:[</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color:'white',</span><br><span class="line">    size:'big',</span><br><span class="line">    id:'1'</span><br><span class="line">&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color:'white',</span><br><span class="line">    size:'small',</span><br><span class="line">    id:'2'</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>后求助社区用<code>script processor</code>解决</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post car/bm/_update_by_query</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">"query"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"match_all"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">"script"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"lang"</span>: <span class="string">"painless"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"source"</span>: <span class="string">"ctx.cars = ctx.cars.stream().filter(x -&gt; !x.id.equals('1')).collect(Collectors.toList())"</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>后面因为会经常调用，所以干脆写了个 script<br>传入 id 到 params，即可。</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">POST _scripts/delete-car</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">"script"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"lang"</span>: <span class="string">"painless"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">"source"</span>: <span class="string">"ctx.cars = ctx.cars.stream().filter(x -&gt; !x.id.equals(params.id)).collect(Collectors.toList())"</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>调用更新如下</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">POST car/bm/_update_by_query</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="attr">"query"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"match"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">"infoid"</span>: <span class="string">"1566882918000"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">"script"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">"id"</span>: <span class="string">"delete-car"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">"params"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">"id"</span>:<span class="string">"1"</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
