  <entry>
    <title>kendoUI for Vue 之DataSource与ListView</title>
    <link href="http://skymilong.cn/2019/04/09/kendoUI%20for%20Vue%20%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A001/"/>
    <id>http://skymilong.cn/2019/04/09/kendoUI for Vue 学习01/</id>
    <published>2019-04-09T07:33:45.041Z</published>
    <updated>2019-08-28T05:40:38.798Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="kendoUI-for-Vue-学习之-DataSource-与-ListView"><a href="#kendoUI-for-Vue-学习之-DataSource-与-ListView" class="headerlink" title="kendoUI for Vue 学习之 DataSource 与 ListView"></a>kendoUI for Vue 学习之 DataSource 与 ListView</h1><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>项目组后面会前后端分离，使用的是另一个项目组正在弄的一个框架，前端 Vue ，需要结合我们正在使用的 kendoUI，然后苦于国内用的人少，所以只好自己摸索了(=，=后端狗一个)。KendoUI 竟然也支持了 Vue，这算是一件好事了。</p><h2 id="DataSource-amp-ListView"><a href="#DataSource-amp-ListView" class="headerlink" title="DataSource &amp; ListView"></a>DataSource &amp; ListView</h2><p>用的最多的东西就是 DataSource 了，不管 ListView 还是 TreeView 或者 Grid。<br>首先引入</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">"@progress/kendo-ui"</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  ListView,</span><br><span class="line">  ListViewInstaller</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">"@progress/kendo-listview-vue-wrapper"</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  DataSource,</span><br><span class="line">  DataSourceInstaller</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">"@progress/kendo-datasource-vue-wrapper"</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Vue.use(DataSourceInstaller);</span><br><span class="line">Vue.use(ListViewInstaller);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在模板里开始用</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">template</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text"</span> @<span class="attr">keyup.enter</span>=<span class="string">"search"</span> <span class="attr">v-model</span>=<span class="string">"keywords"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">kendo-datasource</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">ref</span>=<span class="string">"dataSource"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">:transport</span>=<span class="string">"listViewTransport"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  &gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">kendo-datasource</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">kendo-listview</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">:data-source-ref</span>=<span class="string">"'dataSource'"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">:template</span>=<span class="string">"listTemplate"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">:selectable</span>=<span class="string">"'single'"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  &gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">kendo-listview</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">template</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里的<code>kendo-datasource</code> 可以用官网说的那种方法，直接写<code>props</code>，我呢因为习惯了<code>transport</code>的方式（个人感觉这个好用点），所以就直接这么写了。其实官网文档并没有看到直接弄<code>transport</code>的，我也是凭感觉写的。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">data()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">keywords:<span class="string">''</span>,</span><br><span class="line">listTemplate:  <span class="string">'&lt;div class="xzqhListView" &gt;#:data.XZMC?data.XZMC:data.WGMC#&lt;/div&gt;'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">listViewTransport: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  read: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    url:  <span class="string">"apiv/common-api/getlist"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    cache:  <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    type:  <span class="string">"GET"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    data: <span class="function"><span class="params">()</span>=&gt;</span> &#123;  <span class="comment">//用箭头可以共用this，方便获取keywords</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">var</span>  jsnr  =  <span class="keyword">this</span>.keywords;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span>(jsnr==<span class="string">''</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        jsnr=<span class="string">"*"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        jsnr=<span class="string">"*"</span>+jsnr.toUpperCase()+<span class="string">"*"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">var</span>  params  = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        jsnr:  jsnr,</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span>  params;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">methods:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  search:<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//这里dataSource对应ref的值，kendoWidget()是获取自身实例</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//然后调用read()方法重新获取。请求的params是keywords</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">this</span>.$refs.dataSource.kendoWidget().read();</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>感觉是差不多和原来 Kendo for Vue 的用法差不多吧。然后 listView 这里需要自己绑定模板。<code>:data-source-ref</code> 填<code>dataSource</code>里的<code>ref</code>的值就 OK。我这里是一个简单搜索。记录下学习过程。</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;h1 id=&quot;kendoUI-for-Vue-学习之-DataSource-与-ListView&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#kendoUI-for-Vue-学习之-DataSource-与-ListView&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;kendoUI fo
      
    
    </summary>
    
